{"tid":725033,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"認真想問 點解兩個一直係十年入面霸住金球獎嘅球員唔可以一齊做球皇","createTime":"2018-07-01T12:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T14:06:51.000Z","uid":59491,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2615e7a6700b90213041bdeb5cac4fe29aa527","tid":725033,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"明明講緊兩條友十年入面冇人撼動到佢地金球獎地位 唔係c7就係美斯攞<br />\n仲要講緊十年入面一直破緊記錄<br />\n可以話佢地兩條友都將球王標準推到好高<br />\n<br />\n而舊時班友好多都係一兩季巔峰 反而就係球皇<br />\n或者咁講 冇一個球員可以統治咗球壇咁耐 真係明顯feel到係拋離晒個個時代嘅人<br />\n但兩邊fans都要拗邊個先係唯一球皇 點解唔會承認兩者都係球皇呢<br />\n<br />\n利申 <br />\n講球感一定美斯&gt;c7<br />\n但c7一直嚴格對待自己 連艾夫拿都頂唔順c7啲飲食習慣同訓練心態 呢種職業精神亦值得敬佩"},{"pid":"6f4e0a3e4e76264449dc8e33113c39e913d9e031","tid":725033,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"史尼達 列貝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4bb8f95f97f15c09de0639359738ca2726cbbd","tid":725033,"uid":60766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f4e0a3e4e76264449dc8e33113c39e913d9e031","tid":725033,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"史尼達 列貝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T13:52:34.000Z","msg":"小白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b1c367658469eaac34123b5633b533031128f8","tid":725033,"uid":140802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"兩班fans實會互片<br />\n到佢地退左落黎十年黎就會個個稱頌 上神枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd59f5efb90017c1d4aff04cec4023416709281","tid":725033,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"啲人係想證明自己眼光好啲，自己叻啲姐，唔關兩個球員事。"},{"pid":"84aa837150ae7e448f3aa2c0027ce4e1f54e41e8","tid":725033,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-